data.description: Welcome to the epitome of comfortable living in the charming Del Prado Community of Boulder City! This immaculate single-story home offers everything you've been dreaming of, from a sparkling blue Pool to a fabulous Kitchen. Quaint enclosed poolside Patio attached to an open and flowing floor-plan that exudes Pride of Ownership. Highly upgraded throughout, Newer Roof, A/C, Solar Pool Heater, Saltwater Pool, high-end custom Garage Cabinets and lots more! With nearby Shopping and Schools, a spacious 2-car garage with an additional large Carport, nice Carpet, Tile and real Hardwood flooring throughout this is one you will not want to miss! This corner lot Beauty is move-in ready and perfect for entertaining!
